{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Kickstart your game’s journey to Apple platforms with new agentic skills in Game Porting Toolkit 4 that can dramatically accelerate the process of porting your game. Explore how to work alongside your AI coding assistant to adopt Metal 4, integrate MetalFX, and tune your game for Apple hardware. Find out how agents can autonomously troubleshoot GPU rendering issues using Metal debugging tools, empowering you to focus on what matters most."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc26-357-speedrun-your-game-port-with-agentic-coding"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC26"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC26-357-Speedrun-your-game-port-with-agentic-coding"},"metadata":{"title":"Speedrun your game port with agentic coding","role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC26","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Watch Video (28 min)","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2026\/357"}},"sections":[],"references":{"WWDC26-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC26-Icon.png","type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCN